List of tasks running on the server
- Status : the status and the current progress of the task
- Start : the start date of the task
- Update : the date of the last update of the task
- User : the owner of the task
- Message : the last message (in case of error/cancel, ...)
By default display task ordered by Start DESC.
Clicking on entry open it in a new tab.

By the way, the user can select sample that are not yet ready (still importating).

register corresponding samples and display them in the grid in the previous popup
The upload is still resumable, so if the client is interrupted, the download can be resume.
